branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The VNA series is a universal 2 port valve used for controlling pneumatic systems or air-hydro circuits. Its balanced poppet design permits normal and reverse flow application. Available as external pilot solenoid or air operated.
&lt;/p&gt;

